= PUPPET MODULE:
  vsftpd

== REQUIREMENTS:

=== Platform and Application Environment:

Tested on Ubuntu 12.04.

== USAGE:

# Simple default install

class { 'vsftpd' : }
include vsftpd

# The AntiClass pattern

class { 'vsftpd' : installed => false }

# Fact driven infrastructure. All vsftpd options are entirely fact driven.
# Below are the available vsftpd facts that mirror vsftpd parameters.
# Most of the facts are Boolean but some are Integer and String. Please consult
# the vsftpd.conf man page for more information.

